verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Take time to be holy, speak oft with thy Lord;
Abide in Him always and feed on His word.
Make friends with God’s children,
Help those who are weak,
Forgetting in nothing His blessing to seek.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Take time to be holy, the world rushes on;
Spend much time in secret with Jesus alone.
By looking to Jesus, like Him thou shalt be;
Thy friends in thy conduct His likeness shall see.{/lang-eng}
